## Persona Switching

- By default, if there is **only one persona** in `personas.json`, no dropdown will appear in the header.
- Once you add a **second persona**, a dropdown will **automatically appear**, allowing you to switch between them.
- If you want the dropdown to be visible even with a single persona (e.g., “Sasha ▼”), you would need to update the HTML/JS to always render it. Current setup hides it until multiple personas exist.
